  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Dungeons and Raids</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dungeons and Raids is a gacha game where you will collect heroes and make them fight in the dungeons...</strong> This is an IDLE-GAME!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240520/extras/5bed6cf4ba169fdc646a28999bc05868.avif?t=1762651325\" width=562 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Dungeons and Raids you will be a summoner whom summons champions to fight for you in the dungeons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >fighting dungeon enemies will reward you gold wich can be traded at the Market.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >and  build a unique team </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >that could progress even further in the dungeons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240520/extras/2c1f576cf25801deb3b7a3617afdd6f7.avif?t=1762651325\" width=562 height=104 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Unique Items to be crafted and bought at the Market..</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Move to more difficult levels...</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > No Microtransactions</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > (Game still being worked so more will come)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240520/extras/25e3c24e31efe28b53f55958682090be.avif?t=1762651325\" width=773 height=192 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Dungeons and Raids</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dungeons and Raids is a gacha game where you will collect heroes and make them fight in the dungeons...</strong> This is an IDLE-GAME!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240520/extras/5bed6cf4ba169fdc646a28999bc05868.avif?t=1762651325\" width=562 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Dungeons and Raids you will be a summoner whom summons champions to fight for you in the dungeons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >fighting dungeon enemies will reward you gold wich can be traded at the Market.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >and  build a unique team </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >that could progress even further in the dungeons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240520/extras/2c1f576cf25801deb3b7a3617afdd6f7.avif?t=1762651325\" width=562 height=104 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Unique Items to be crafted and bought at the Market..</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Move to more difficult levels...</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > No Microtransactions</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > (Game still being worked so more will come)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2240520/extras/25e3c24e31efe28b53f55958682090be.avif?t=1762651325\" width=773 height=192 /></span></p>",
